Looking at the provided problem, the "Net Profit" line item is clearly listed under "Cash Flow From Operating Activities" with an amount of "-1401436.89" on the date "2024-01-30".

2. In the given cash flow statement, "Net Profit" is listed with the value "-1401436.89".
3. Therefore, the value to be extracted is "-1401436.89".
